body:
DO NOT act like a victim when one or more team mates won&#039;t have it!

I have had LITERALLY EVERY game I&#039;ve tried to play today ruined before they start  by an auto locking double jg Warwick, An auto locked ADC Warwick, An Auto locked SUPPORT WARWICK 4 TIMES!

All say the same things as well. &quot; It&#039;s just normal&quot;, &quot;Don&#039;t play blinds then&quot;, &quot;It&#039;s not trolling to play what I want&quot;, &quot;I&#039;m better then you&quot;

Then when You call the same standard, IE; &quot;Fine I&#039;ll play how I want then&quot; they all respond with &quot;OMG REPORT *** TROLLING&quot; &quot;Don&#039;t play If you cant deal with off meta picks!&quot;, &quot;Warwick support is OP1 What&#039;s your problem!&quot;

What&#039;s my problem? This happens EVERY TIME a new champ is released, but I have NEVER seen it this bad! not even with EKKO! I&#039;ve dodged 3 games today to avoid troll comps and the 4 I have played have all had a this happen! Then they get offended and play the victim in all chat! 

Case and point? You want to paly the new champ SOOOOOOOO badly that you&#039;re willing to sabotage a game before it starts? Don&#039;t be surprised when someone whos had enough isn&#039;t in the mood to deal with it and take yer loss like the good sport you likely CLAIM to be!
